    <item>
      <title>美联储最新工具在降息押注上变得更具吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/fed-s-newest-tool-has-become-more-attractive-amid-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储上周转向鸽派立场后，今年三月为支持陷入困境的银行而制定的贷款工具看起来比以往任何时候都更好，因为大幅降息的预期使利率更具吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/fed-s-newest-tool-has-become-more-attractive-amid-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 16:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
